{"tid":873611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩從澳門返黎，發現澳門d中文字已經全部變曬殘體字","createTime":"2018-10-23T14:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T19:30:35.000Z","uid":120678,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a5dd8dcd3023333587751036e02837d628b85d99","tid":873611,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:27:12.000Z","msg":"Taipa果邊d新賭場，乜金沙城中心、威尼斯人、巴黎人、新濠天地、銀河，入面路牌同宣傳單張等用既中文已經全部係殘體字<br />\n以為舊賭場會好d，點知返到舊城區既葡京都係一樣，d牌同穿梭巴士上面個路線牌全部都殘體<br />\n睇完之後好心寒，好驚香港有一日都會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90a41d1a798af1bc8101b262d74b26c397f9615","tid":873611,"uid":23707,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"你真係好耐無去過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2e5e688338a46f6ebaa71d6a790780331a7d29","tid":873611,"uid":31237,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"岩你老母"},{"pid":"e2a2263b62ef19b978a9d34d8d4d500cd93a3b7e","tid":873611,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"路氹不嬲都冇咩本地人去<br />\n<br />\n不過內港間中都見到招牌寫殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a85d7c7fdc89e8be828d38016c20dc51ff70577","tid":873611,"uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d90a41d1a798af1bc8101b262d74b26c397f9615","tid":873611,"uid":23707,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"你真係好耐無去過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"自己本身唔賭錢，葡國野香港都有得食，所以好少會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caa1ca75fde8c9f1c8f65cc3c4ccfbf0dcb7895","tid":873611,"uid":56701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:35:58.000Z","msg":"中國人一有錢派就乜都唔理，仲點會理用咩字體"},{"pid":"499717e9d1d3da0a0b17ace7afc0841e85943cbe","tid":873611,"uid":152598,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"根本去澳門同去大陸有咩分別<br />\n根本一樣<br />\n你聞下呼吸嘅空氣都同返大陸陣味係一樣"},{"pid":"6129733c1dcd8a473bc8e1b98031a01d43505de7","tid":873611,"uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"好耐之前已經係咁"},{"pid":"cb82c289337e78f7bcf784a96168a2a038e9e05f","tid":873611,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"499717e9d1d3da0a0b17ace7afc0841e85943cbe","tid":873611,"uid":152598,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"根本去澳門同去大陸有咩分別<br />\n根本一樣<br />\n你聞下呼吸嘅空氣都同返大陸陣味係一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"我咁睇，填海區就似強國<br />\n舊區都仲正常dd，不過都開始畀遊客入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59332924a03b459b73cc3f42421f12e3d52f355","tid":873611,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"好彩香港仲未比殘體入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c7e618951e3c9aa6c23cea82662b68f165d058","tid":873611,"uid":3093,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"我7年冇去過澳門，上星期六去完一轉返黎<br />\n好多地方用左簡體字，有啲依然用繁體字，但寫出黎啲文法、用語都係蝗語<br />\n周圍都係粗聲粗氣嘅大陸人，雖然我知佢地好多都有錢過我<br />\n但唔知點解喺條街度行係有啲心慌慌嘅感覺"},{"pid":"8c896df388c35ac46b4a132f2e66dfe700a6bcf7","tid":873611,"uid":61271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"對於班奴才，邊個比錢邊個就係主人<br />\n而家多支那人消費，咪要跪低寫簡體字迎合佢地囉<br />\n<br />\n亦都唔使擔心香港啦，每日百五隻蝗蟲入侵香港，之前都係見啲小學生講普通話，早兩日連中學生都係，好快成個社會就蝗化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d267006025e39b53123a9952cafb51d0847745","tid":873611,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T18:54:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a1669669dfe926f3c4bc895c75ea289dc9dca6a","tid":873611,"uid":197920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e59332924a03b459b73cc3f42421f12e3d52f355","tid":873611,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"好彩香港仲未比殘體入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T19:06:50.000Z","msg":"Just the matter of time <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ec8ecaede88ea824c7dd065cb896790db6ec2d","tid":873611,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T19:24:50.000Z","msg":"坐咗幾多年？"},{"pid":"f974ebf91de31bce64199578c1c0f2b2f60c5bc2","tid":873611,"uid":43921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T19:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一街外勞 新移民<br />\n本地人放假街都唔想出"},{"pid":"597f86613782ce16a9d3e5f6a487754d3e9ea57d","tid":873611,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T19:30:35.000Z","msg":"珠海市澳門區丶路氹區"}]}